 <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"text-align: left;color: rgb(27, 42, 139);letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刘金松、陈雪珂：</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&amp;mid=2650990722&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a856d7b76d06da38aaed545f5a16b382&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"《拉布布走红启示，数字时代文化IP孵化新密码》\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">《拉布布走红启示，数字时代文化IP孵化新密码》</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-align: left;color: rgb(27, 42, 139);letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">张宗艺、童祁：</span></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&amp;mid=2650969509&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=758848b8af01273b859c3711eeab82c7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"《如何复制下一个淄博？》\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">《如何复制下一个淄博？》</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\">\n    <br>\n   </span></p>\n  <p class=\"js_darkmode__16\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0em;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"281\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4856348470806302\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" dat